title: Cradle of Rome 2: Premium v1.1
description:
Journey through 100 levels of matching fun and exhilarating city-building in Cradle of Rome 2! Match three or more tiles and experience Rome's development, from small settlement to flourishing empire. Discover all-new game modes and earn trophies for your various skills. Beat challenging mini-games, draw up brilliant blueprints, and become the Emperor in Cradle of Rome 2!
